<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.5">
<l>pollāk kuṟaḷuruvāyp poṟkaiyil nīrēṟ</l>
<l>ṟellā vulaku maḷantukoṇṭa vemperumāṉ</l>
<l>nallārkaḷ vāḻum naḷiraraṅka nākaṇaiyā</l>
<l>ṉillātōṅ kaipporuḷu meytuvā ṉottuḷaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Lord who—taking the form of a wicked dwarf</l>
<l>and accepting water in [His] golden hands—took all the worlds by measuring [them],</l>
<l>He who lies on the serpent-bed in the cool Raṅgam where the good people live</l>
<l>Is as if He would acquire the objects from the hands of us people who have nothing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
